{"tid":2054568,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【國金89樓】港人存款「送中」 買三線城市地方債","createTime":"2020-06-07T09:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T09:45:04.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e75f81279270ac49835a94e01a521f5a48d295d4","tid":2054568,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T09:10:39.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯翻開年報，集友銀行自XIB入手後，信貸快速膨脹，客戶貸款由2018年的484億，急升至2019年的760億元，升276億元或57%，遠超過行業同期。<br />\n<br />\n至於內地風險相關貸款比例，亦由2018年底僅11%（53億元）飇升至去年底的34%（258億元），即短短一年這間蚊型銀行，竟然借多200億元予內地，而資金來源主要是港人存款，這亦是新股東XIB買入集友銀行目的。<br />\n<br />\n再觀察其債券及存款證投資變化，由2018年的賬面值265億元升至2019年的447億元，升幅達182億元。當然集友會辯解信貸總量升幅與風險未必成正比，信貸評級亦是A1以上較多，惟評級只是Mapping標普&mdash;&mdash;不少發債公司僅聘請內地評級機構，未必符合國際標準。<br />\n<br />\n究竟集友借出的是甚麼類型、行業貸款？本總裁從機密文件獲悉不少是讓海外投資者聞風喪膽的地方債，主要投資大型城鎮基建，涉逾30間公司，規模最少百億，在銀行內部稱為「市政貸款」⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200606/FJ4FJBRDQPPAGZNOEBEXYSZOEY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200606%2FFJ4FJBRDQPPAGZNOEBEXYSZOEY%2F&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUnwORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=c7c35912\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200606%2FFJ4FJBRDQPPAGZNOEBEXYSZOEY%2F&h=2e33443e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200606/FJ4FJBRDQPPAGZNOEBEXYSZOEY/</a>"},{"pid":"e2e3749c233842efba34706a076561d3a3c1dc48","tid":2054568,"uid":153151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T09:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xz0C0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xz0C0n.jpg&h=7b7d0741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djateT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djateT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8a46894d1d4a02367ab8e60b1c798f5c09d41e5a","tid":2054568,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":